    • deleteByIdGtNet

      @Modifying @Query("DELETE FROM GTNetSupplierDetail d WHERE d.gtNetConfig.idGtNet = ?1") void deleteByIdGtNet(Integer idGtNet)
      Deletes all GTNetSupplierDetail entries for a specific GTNet peer. Used during full recreation mode to clear existing entries before creating new ones.
      Parameters:
      idGtNet - the GTNet peer ID whose supplier details should be deleted

    • findByEntityKindAndInstrumentIds

      @Query("SELECT d FROM GTNetSupplierDetail d WHERE d.entityKind = ?1 AND d.securitycurrency.idSecuritycurrency IN ?2") List<GTNetSupplierDetail> findByEntityKindAndInstrumentIds(byte entityKind, List<Integer> idSecuritycurrencies)
      Finds all GTNetSupplierDetail entries for given instruments and entity kind. Used for filtering instruments when querying AC_OPEN suppliers, ensuring that only instruments a supplier is known to support are sent in requests.
      Parameters:
      entityKind - the entity kind (0=LAST_PRICE, 1=HISTORICAL_PRICES)
      idSecuritycurrencies - list of instrument IDs to check
      Returns:
      list of supplier details matching the criteria
